org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface Shape

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Figure, Primitive
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Arc, Ellipse, Line, Rectangle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArcImpl, EllipseImpl, LineImpl, RectangleImpl, ShapeImpl

    public interface Shape
extends Figure
    A representation of the model object 'Shape'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Line Width
    • Antialias
    • Alpha
    • Fill
    • Outline

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getShape()
